description:
This is a 33 minute workout called '30 Minute Full Body Dumbbell Strength Workout [All Standing/No Repeat]' from the channel Juice & Toya.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Tap in with us for another Full Body Strength Workout that will leave you feeling pumped! We will take you through 3 groups of 7 exercises that are  different but similar variations of each other. All you'll need for this workout is a pair or multiple sets of dumbbells to challenge you with each exercise. There are some included modifications to ensure that most fitness levels can complete this workout. Each of the exercises are low impact so its great if you live in an apartment/condo or if you have any bone/joint limitations. As always give this workout a try and let us know how you did!
